snippet.title: Winnie the Pooh and all all JAVA GAME (Deep Wireless Concepts 2007) FULL WALKTHROUGH
snippet.description:
"Winnie the Poo" - Where Piglet and I are going - a big, big secret! Your favorite childhood heroes are now in your cell phone. Help Winnie the Pooh and Piglet go through the forest, collect pots of honey, visit Rabbit and wish Donkey Eeyore his birthday. In the forest, you'll be surrounded by its unfriendly inhabitants - harmful snails, nasty frogs and vicious running stumps. Throw them cones and make your way to the cherished hive of honey! Why in the world is there honey? For Pooh to eat it! Where there's honey, there are the wrong bees, but Piglet and his gun will not let the bear cub go to waste! Who goes to visit in the morning - that's the wise thing to do! You can get a good meal in the Rabbit's hole, but then you'll be able to get back down it! Finally, after all the fun adventures Winnie the Pooh and Piglet need to congratulate his sad friend, Donkey Eeyore. So, wish you happiness in your personal life, Pooh!

The game is entirely in Russian.
